      "raw_text": "At last nights meeting Of the city\ncouncil, in committee of the whole,\nto consider the appropriations for\nthe coming year, the following mo-\nton was introduced and passed:\n\n\n\"That the corporation counsel\nfurnish the council with an opn-\nion as to whether the Washington\nWater Power company could be\ncompelled under it's franchise to\nrebuild or repair the third Howard\nstreet BRIDGE\"\n\n\nThe ordinary, everyday taxpayer\nwould like to know what this reso-\nluton means. The franchise pre-\nscented to the Washington. Water\nPower company by our evergreen\nGus council, and for which not even\npromise was given, calls for re\npairs to the third channel bridge\non Howard street if necessary to\nmake 1t safe for street car pur-\nposes."
    }
  ]
